382
00:29:53,680 --> 00:29:54,880
Pronto.

383
00:29:55,480 --> 00:29:57,920
Sentem-se aí, as duas.

384
00:29:58,000 --> 00:29:59,040
Aí.

385
00:30:00,000 --> 00:30:05,120
