386
00:30:05,920 --> 00:30:07,640
acumulo.

387
00:30:07,720 --> 00:30:08,800
Senhora...

388
00:30:09,480 --> 00:30:10,320
Sra. Daugeron?

389
00:30:10,920 --> 00:30:12,000
Aqui.

390
00:30:17,200 --> 00:30:18,080
Pegue.

391
00:30:20,800 --> 00:30:22,160
