464
00:37:15,880 --> 00:37:16,760
Porra.

465
00:37:16,840 --> 00:37:18,960
-Emma! Emma, espere! 
-Merda!

466
00:37:19,040 --> 00:37:20,680
Emma, espere!

467
00:37:21,720 --> 00:37:23,040
Emma!

